message: Initial Commit of new Octopus Library.
Fixed typos in comments. Added bin to .gitignore
Added JaCoCo test coverage. Implemented as ant target called 'coverage'. Will generate coverage html report in test/reports/coverage.
Major changes to Job API. Its structure is now closer to the Files API.
Do not throw away *.class files. But keep in classes/ directory.
Do not group adaptors on core  additional and unstable directories  but use ant to group adaptors.
Converted engine.Adaptor from interface to abstract class. Removed RECURSIVE from CopyOptions  since no adaptors support it. Added recursiveCopy to FileUtils.
first version that can create sessions and channels
For code coverage the classes and sources for the local adaptor could not be found.
Added exceptions to Adaptor.filesAdaptor() and Adaptors.jobsAdaptor()
Add class/module diagrams to javadoc using https://code.google.com/p/apiviz/
Added properties checking to Adaptor base class. Reformatted to adhere to official NLeSC java codestyle.
Added default properties to the octopus engine.
Refactor of certificate support  make it a first-class citizen.
Adaptor class loader now check for "octopus.adaptor.load" property.
Adaptor class loader now tests for adaptor names to load.
Fixed test to use lower case adaptor names
Changed adaptor loading scheme to use lower case names for adaptors.
Add tests which use mockito to mock.
Added implementations of getStatus and cancel in LocalAdaptor. Added JobStatus implementation.
Added specialized "supports(String scheme)" call to local adaptor that accepts null as a valid scheme.
Add mockito library for mocking in unit tests.
We don't use powermock. So remove it's jar.
Add test coverage for ssh adaptor.
Add documentation how to add a new adaptor to the build chain.
Added support for public/private key pairs  known_hosts file. First integration test now works.
Moved Eclipse Java Formatter and clean Up xml files to https://github.com/NLeSC/wiki/wiki/Eclipe .
Rename package nl.esciencecenter.octopus.tests to nl.esciencecenter.octopus in src/ directory. Fixes #10.
Almost complete overhaul of API. Should be almost OK now...
Merge branch 'develop' of ssh://git@github.com/NLeSC/octopus.git into develop
Fixed most bugs in test classes.
working on caching of ssh connections
Working on parsing xml output of SGE. The approach used now relies on the xml schema  which unfortunatelly doesn't match the actual output very well.
Rename tests so method name of test say <method under test>_<start state>_<expected behavior>.
Converted Path to RelativePath and AbsolutePath. Moved OctopusProperties to engine.
Merge branch 'develop' of ssh://github.com/NLeSC/octopus into develop
in progress: new qstat parsing approach
Changed newPath to use RelativePath instead of String. Added newPath with multiple relative paths as parameter.
Removed getUniqueID from public interface of FileSystem and Scheduler
Added exceptions to files()  jobs()  credentials() calls in Adaptor.
Merged Jason's API changes  everything compiles again.
Merge branch 'develop' of ssh://github.com/NLeSC/octopus into develop
Added copy constructor to RelativePath. Added constructor to AbsolutePathImplementation that accepts multiple RelativePaths.
Switched default entry point of local file system to user.home.
Fixed local FileSystem creation. Fixed local createDirectory.
Fixed OctopusProperties to check if a key exists.
Local jobs adaptor needs 'local:///' as location.
Fixed local scheduler implementation to correctly compare to job scheduler.
Fixed ParallelProcess to work without stdin.
FileEngine now forward all calls to adaptors. No shortcuts allowed.
Refactored PathAttribute to PathAttributePair Refactored AbstractPathAttribute to PathAttributePairImplementation
Fixed LocalJobExecutor to correctly set done. Fixed SandboxedLocalJobIT to delete files after test.
Added hashcode and equals to RelativePath.
Added getLocalScheduler()  and changed local implementation accordingly.
Renamed adaptor to gridengine QstatOutputParser now reads most qstat files Added a test dir to the gridengine adaptor Added a bunch of tests for the QstatOutputParser
Added QueueStatus + the needed getters in Jobs.
Fixed double close in ssh inputstream

Added a QueueStatusImplementation to the jobs engine package. Fixed gridengine adaptor build script. Finished all the gridengine adaptor queue info commands. Also throw a OctopusIOException to the getQueueStatus functions in Jobs.
small fix to accomodate change to api
Replace OctopusRuntimeException with UnsupportedOperationException  because some methods immutable object are unsupported.
Add test for getLongProperty  getShortProperty  getDoubleProperty  getFloatProperty .
cleanup of ssh adaptor: fileSystemImpl is not subclassed anymore
Throw more specific exceptions  set properties for known_hosts and strict host key checking.
Added Javadoc to part of the public API.
Added job submission to GridEngine adaptor
Merge branch 'develop' of ssh://github.com/NLeSC/octopus into develop
Added OctopusIOException to all calls in Jobs
JavaDoc of Files should be complete.
Fixed copy without copy options  implemented move  fixed bug in dir streams.
JavaDoc for Jobs should be complete.
Added JavaDoc to jobs package. Should be reasonably complete.
Added Javadoc to files package (not complete).
New Generic File Integration Test. Tests basic FileSystem manipulations.
Structure of ssh job adaptor is now ok.
Fixed compiler error due to interface change.
Added JavaDoc to most of files package. Some issues left.
Added hasDetachedJobs and hasLocalStandardStreams to Scheduler.
First complete version of ssh jobs
Fixed Scheduler close for local adaptor.
Throw a detailed Exception if possible.
Refactoring txt parsing into seperate class
Added tests for recursiveCopy with file already exists errors.
